xtras/af2c2d0b264cdf2c7d345ec77b189418.webm?t=1774340685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1396190/extras/af2c2d0b264cdf2c7d345ec77b189418.mp4?t=1774340685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>A Reflection about Death and the Afterlife</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Death tends to be a taboo subject. With DE-EXIT, we aim to initiate a discussion on these fascinating topics from a more positive perspective than we typically do. You will be able to experience and hear about death from plenty of different perspectives. We hope that you will enjoy our ode to life. </p>",
